  "detailed_description": "Create your character and survive wave after wave of zombies! <br>Gain exp, level up and unlock new skills.<br>Visit the shop between waves to buy weapons, ammo and other useful items.<br>Explore further to get exp bonuses and better loot.<br>How many Zeds can you kill before your inevitable demise?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Character customization menu<br></li><li> Exp levelling system<br></li><li> Increasingly difficult wave based survival<br></li><li> 10+ different Zombie Types<br></li><li> 20+ Weapons<br></li><li> Turrets<br></li><li> Different rarities for weapons (eg. Common, Rare, Legendary)<br></li><li> Throwables such as Grenades, Throwing Knives, Molotovs<br></li><li> 4 Different stages with different \"boss rounds\"<br></li><li> A shop to buy weapons, ammo and more!</li></ul>",
